    Cascade --> Audit

    N2 -.evt 写入.-> TBL1
    N2 -.edge 写入.-> TBL2

    Cascade --> TBL3
    Audit --> TBL5
    RB --> TBL4

    Audit --> Fix
    ROLL -.修复.-> Cascade
    ACC -.继续.-> Cascade
    MAN -.人工介入.-> Cascade

    classDef trigger fill:#E94B6A,color:#fff,stroke:#A52A2A,stroke-width:2px
    classDef node fill:#F5A623,color:#fff,stroke:#B07516,stroke-width:2px
    classDef cascade fill:#9B59B6,color:#fff,stroke:#5B2C6F,stroke-width:2px
    classDef audit fill:#3498DB,color:#fff,stroke:#1F618D,stroke-width:2px
    classDef db fill:#50C878,color:#fff,stroke:#2D7A4D,stroke-width:2px
    classDef fix fill:#F39C12,color:#fff,stroke:#9C640D,stroke-width:2px

    class EVT trigger
    class N1,N2,N3,N4 node
    class R1,R2,R3,R4,C1,C2,C3,C4 cascade
    class LOG,RB,DIFF audit
    class TBL1,TBL2,TBL3,TBL4,TBL5,DB db
    class ROLL,ACC,MAN fix

    %% 关键设计标注（PPT 讲到这里时口头解释）
    %% [1] 4 维实体节点 + 边关系 · 跨卷一致性可视化
    %% [2] Backfill 自动反推 · 不靠手工补全 (16 tests · 4 Extractor + 1 Backfiller)
